    "tha-ap537:11.3_0": "Kassapa the Prince:",
    "tha-ap537:11.4_0": "but his disciple is truly the Teacher.",
    "tha-ap537:12.1_0": "My mind is released from limits:",
    "tha-ap537:12.2_0": "And the precious things as precious,",
    "tha-ap537:12.3_0": "Your minds",
