    "tha-ap537:14.2_0": "as the sky rains, the lions roar,",
    "tha-ap537:14.3_0": "As a consequence I’m rid of barrier,",
    "tha-ap537:14.4_0": "of the lame, one-eyed she-goat.",
    "tha-ap537:15.1_0": "whose belly is cut off,",
    "tha-ap537:15.2_0": "and I had been sentenced to the Vajjis.",
    "tha-ap537:15.3_0": "But because of her mother and father,",
    "tha-ap537:15.4_0": "for refuge to Nigrodha.",
    "tha-ap537:16.1_0": "With that deer range,",
    "tha-ap537:16.2_0": "killed living creatures;",
    "tha-ap537:16.3_0": "Having given up killing,",
    "tha-ap537:16.4_0": "I was responsible.",
    "tha-ap537:17.1_0": "“One should cultivate yourself,",
    "tha-ap537:17.2_0": "and I’m not smeared with poison.",
    "tha-ap537:17.3_0": "Nigrodha is better for him,",
    "tha-ap537:17.4_0": "than life.’",
    "tha-ap537:18.1_0": "Then that fearing the deer,",
