    "tha-ap537:19.3_0": "Seping a rocky mountain,",
    "tha-ap537:19.4_0": "I’ve enjoyed the victor’s instruction.",
    "tha-ap537:2.1_0": "When I became a brahmin,",
    "tha-ap537:2.2_0": "unselfish, with no need for hope,",
    "tha-ap537:2.3_0": "Living for the day’s meditation,",
    "tha-ap537:2.4_0": "and he saw the world speedless.",
    "tha-ap537:20.1_0": "Now I’ll now be his right here in Rājagaha,",
