    "tha-ap537:25.2_0": "by not grasping at all,",
    "tha-ap537:25.3_0": "I tamed myself,",
    "tha-ap537:25.4_0": "best of men.",
    "tha-ap537:26.1_0": "My defilements have been burnt away by practicing absorption—",
    "tha-ap537:26.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "tha-ap537:26.3_0": "and live without defilements.",
    "tha-ap537:27.1_0": "It was truly for me",
    "tha-ap537:27.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "tha-ap537:27.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "tha-ap537:28.1_0": "Attaining the four kinds of textual analysis",
    "tha-ap537:28.2_0": "... “I attained the noble ones,” ...",
    "tha-ap537:28.3_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "tha-ap537:29.1_0": "That is how these verses were recited by the senior venerable Kassapa the senior venerable Kassapa.",
    "tha-ap537:3.1_0": "they reveal it really do,",
    "tha-ap537:3.2_0": "by those who speak to,",
    "tha-ap537:3.3_0": "Disciplined mind,",
    "tha-ap537:3.4_0": "a large, steep cliff.",
    "tha-ap537:30.1_0": "the fifth substance.",
    "tha-ap537:30.2_0": "is twenty-four shared out.",
    "tha-ap537:4.1_0": "Then my mind unified,",
    "tha-ap537:4.2_0": "after being invited,",
    "tha-ap537:4.3_0": "Overcome by different words,",
    "tha-ap537:4.4_0": "felt humiliated.",
    "tha-ap537:5.1_0": "with many different flocks of birds.",
    "tha-ap537:5.2_0": "presented me to the pillar.",
    "tha-ap537:5.3_0": "I was seven days old,",
    "tha-ap537:5.4_0": "frequented by food and drinks.",
    "tha-ap537:6.1_0": "With different flowers,",
    "tha-ap537:6.2_0": "I offered a meal.",
    "tha-ap537:6.3_0": "I’ve left behind the foot,",
    "tha-ap537:6.4_0": "I became confident.",
    "tha-ap537:7.1_0": "a sage says that",
